          <Box></Box>
        </Product>
        <Product>
          <ImageProduct src={imageproduct2}></ImageProduct>
          <Box></Box>
        </Product>
        <Product>
          <ImageProduct src={imageproduct2}></ImageProduct>
          <Box>
            <TextBox>How to create mobile-optimized</TextBox>
          </Box>
          <GoButton src/>

      </ProductWrapper>
    </BannerWrapper>
  );
}
